\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

 : single-valued operator on 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{R}^{n}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

 is firmly nonexpansive on 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{R}^{n}$
\end_inset

 if 
\begin_inset Formula $(2T-I_{n})$
\end_inset

 is nonexpansive
\end_layout

