\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{R}$
\end_inset

 from being a nonexpansive operator over the sequence 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \left(z_{n},z\right)\right\} _{n\in\mathbf{N}}$
\end_inset

 is zero
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
our convergence proof coincides with known convergence results for convex
 setup
\begin_inset Note Note
