\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
is it possible to establish convergence NC-ADMM ignoring NC-DRS?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
our convergence analysis is established for 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
nonempty, compact, but not necessarily convex constraint sets
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
it is equally applicable to the smaller subclass of problems with convex
 constraint sets
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
in this smaller subclass of convex problems NC-ADMM and NC-DRS have the
 same convergence properties
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
